author: @NgocAnh-wr9bo
text: Since the news came out, I thought what can I do to concentrate, this is a shock to me as well as the entire Bunnies, I believe. NewJeans' launch date is July 22, 2022. That day, 5 unknown girls debuted to the world with the MV "Attention", followed by songs that impressed everyone. I discovered NewJeans on July 28, 2022, the first thing that attracted me was their new music. However, the deeper I dig, the more I love these 5 girls with lovely, sociable personalities, who are indispensable pieces that make up NewJeans. For nearly 2 years now, my love for NewJeans has only grown more. Maybe I missed the opportunity to stream the debut MV for you guys in the first 24 hours, but after that, MV Ditto, OMG, album "Get up", teaser "Bubble Gum", I always watch every minute to wait for the MV. Play the action and try to be one of the first to watch the video. NewJeans is my comfort, the motivation for me to try hard to study, I always remind myself: "You have to study well to make a lot of money and go to NewJeans concerts, sing NewJeans songs with Bunnies ". I really love NewJeans, since I heard the news, I can't concentrate on doing anything, I'm worried about my 5 girls, for the fans who like NewJeans' music, I don't know how they will feel when this news comes , but for me, I love music but love all 5 girls, love their personalities, love their talents, love the way NewJeans treats people, I am Bunnies Vietnam, but I want to express my feelings in English, so that if NewJeans read it and international Bunnies, they will know that Bunnies Vietnam is always here and overcomes the storm with NewJeans. ğŸ°ğŸ°ğŸ°ğŸ°ğŸ°ğŸ€ğŸŒ»
